            <V n="text" t="variation">
              <U n="variation">
                <L n="variations">
                  <T>0xF531730C<!--String: "You can't talk about Bellacorde without mentioning us, the Capps. We're the oldest and most distinguished of its families. Everyone looks up to us as an example of chivalry and unity."--></T>
                  <T>0x4CFFEFB5<!--String: "Bellacorde: power, elegance and virtue. Those are our core beliefs. Oh, and designer shoes."--></T>
                  <T>0xB0662535<!--String: "We love a romantic gesture in Bellacorde. We like to say you can't present yourself to a date without a rose.\nSome people say we're too much. But it's just a rose, how much could it cost? 1000 Simoleons?"--></T>
                  <T>0xEF3D63D0<!--String: "In Bellacorde we're bound by honor. We're bound by pride. We're bound by <i>good taste</i>. It's a full-time job being a role model."--></T>
                  <T>0x4ED4A47<!--String: "Us Capps are an old, refined lineage—it was our family that built Bellacorde into what it is today. We try to never forget who we are, and what we're worth. After all, everyone wants to be us."--></T>
                  <T>0xFBAF19BB<!--String: "Bellacorde represents us and we represent Bellacorde. Therefore we <i>must</i> always look impeccable...so that Commoners may aspire to be just like us."--></T>
                </L>
              </U>
            </V>
          </U>
        </V>
      </U>
    </V>
    <V t="buff">
